HEADWORD: crottal
<hw>crottal</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>any of several lichens of the genus
Parmelia from which reddish brown or purple dyes are made.</def>
<altsp>[Also spelled <asp>crottle</asp> and
<asp>crotal</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
